svg.title: comparison of model railway scales
svg.desc: A 242A1 locomotive and standard gauge railway with concrete ties at some rail transport modelling scales by CMG Lee. The images are from http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:242_DEL_Chapelon.jpg and http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Pioneer_plaque_humans.svg , and the engine wheelbase is from http://steamlocomotive.com/locobase.php?country=France&wheel=4-8-4&railroad=sncf .
